React > Frontend framework that help to single page application using
component based structure

/////////////////////////////////
Step to generate React App
///////////////////////////////////////
> open the cmd go inside the folder
> npx create-react-app firstapp

////////////
class
> Logical Component
> We can maintain the state
> maintain logical, call api and even display
funtional
> Dumb Component
> We Cannot maintain State
> Mainly use for display

hooks


////////
State
> Act like a local variable
> Every component can have its own state
> We can update the value of state
> Any Data interaction will happen through state 

Props
> Help to transfer data between 2 nested component
> We cannot update value of props

parent > child (props)
child > parent (props with function)


npm i react-router-dom
npm i react-router-dom@5.3.0

